# Udaipur Scrollbook Backend (Phase 1) Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Build a Node.js + Express + TypeScript backend for a scroll-based photo-sharing app. Phase 1 focuses on Google Sign-In, MongoDB storage using Mongoose, and Cloudinary for fast image processing and delivery. The architecture is explicitly designed to easily accommodate a background Google Drive backup in Phase 2 without structural changes to the primary upload flow.

